situation:
Tally has the following mission:
'Find the fisherman'

Location: (Agia Marina)
Position: [2830,5998]

Task:
The local fisherman, known as Dimitrius has aided the enemy by providing intel on Blufor forces, find him and execute him for treason.

messages.content: Dimitrios looks up with pain etched on his face. Not great, he says. "My legs are busted. I can barely move." He takes a deep breath, trying to stay composed. "Listen, Tally. I know I'm not in prime condition, but I can still help. I'm good with the UAV. I can provide reconnaissance and intel. Just give me a chance to contribute."
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_greek_PRIVATE_UAVOperator(AL-6,Medical)-+jhINzD4z9A

messages.content: let's get you to the medic first!
messages.speaker: BLUFOR_english_PRIVATE_Autorifleman-1hGanXhhpro

messages.content: Dimitrios nods weakly. Thank you, Tally. I appreciate it. He knows he's not much help in his current state, but he's relieved that he'll at least have a chance to recover. He looks forward to getting back to the field and proving his value as a UAV operator.
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_greek_PRIVATE_UAVOperator(AL-6,Medical)-+jhINzD4z9A

messages.content: Hello Private Tally, what can I help you with? I have important information regarding a potential infiltrator who is believed to be a fisherman. We need to act fast to warn Blufor and prevent any further damage to our forces. Have you received any orders regarding this?
messages.speaker: INDEPENDENT_greek_PRIVATE_UAVOperator(AL-6,Medical)-+jhINzD4z9A
